      <title>动荡的一年影响了 Worldline 的盈利，该公司将筹集新债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/worldline-to-raise-new-debt-after-tumultuous-year-hurts-earnings</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Worldline SA 已开始进行再融资，这将增加这家陷入困境的金融科技公司的利息费用，但会带来一些急需的现金以帮助偿还即将到期的债务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/worldline-to-raise-new-debt-after-tumultuous-year-hurts-earnings</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 11:09:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>LVMH Scion 制定计划，助力巴黎足球俱乐部登上巅峰</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/lvmh-scion-lays-out-plan-to-bring-paris-football-club-to-the-top</link>
      <description><![CDATA[安托万·阿诺（Antoine Arnault）是其父亲领导的 LVMH 奢侈品帝国的继承人，他计划将二级足球俱乐部巴黎足球俱乐部打造成卡塔尔支持的巴黎圣日耳曼足球俱乐部的竞争对手。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/lvmh-scion-lays-out-plan-to-bring-paris-football-club-to-the-top</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 10:40:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿里巴巴任命新首席执行官 重组停滞不前的商业部门</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/alibaba-anoints-new-e-commerce-chief-in-overhaul-of-stalling-arm</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿里巴巴集团控股有限公司任命一位资深高管负责整个在线电子商务业务，启动对这家规模庞大但陷入困境的业务的重大改革。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/alibaba-anoints-new-e-commerce-chief-in-overhaul-of-stalling-arm</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 10:25:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据称 Uber 正就投资中国小马智行美国 IPO 进行洽谈</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/uber-said-to-be-in-talks-to-invest-in-us-ipo-of-china-s-pony-ai</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，优步科技公司 (Uber Technologies Inc.) 计划投资小马智行 (Pony AI Inc.) 在美国的首次公开募股 (IPO)，该公司预计将于下周在被这家自动驾驶公司提高规模后确定发行价。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/uber-said-to-be-in-talks-to-invest-in-us-ipo-of-china-s-pony-ai</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 10:09:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Klarna 计划上市为更多金融科技公司上市奠定基础</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/klarna-s-planned-ipo-sets-the-stage-for-more-fintech-listings</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Klarna Bank AB 计划进行的首次公开募股 (IPO) 引发了人们对金融科技公司上市长期低迷的希望，预示着未来几年该行业将出现一波首次公开募股浪潮。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/klarna-s-planned-ipo-sets-the-stage-for-more-fintech-listings</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苹果竞争对手 Oppo 押注中国以外的市场以寻求新增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/apple-rival-oppo-bets-on-markets-beyond-china-for-fresh-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国智能手机制造商 Oppo 正在推动海外增长，寻求新的收入来源，因为其本土市场正面临经济放缓和激烈的竞争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/apple-rival-oppo-bets-on-markets-beyond-china-for-fresh-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 09:49:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Clear 在机场的主导地位可能即将终结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-11-21/clear-use-is-down-in-major-airports-as-service-loses-luster</link>
      <description><![CDATA[这家科技公司目前已成为美国机场安全部门事实上的分支机构，面临着与 TSA、机场和客户之间的问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-11-21/clear-use-is-down-in-major-airports-as-service-loses-luster</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 09:45:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
