    <item>
      <title>中国券商富途因全球战略转变裁员 5%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/chinese-broker-futu-cuts-5-of-staff-as-global-expansion-slows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国互联网券商富途控股有限公司正在重新评估公司的全球扩张战略，计划裁员约 5%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/chinese-broker-futu-cuts-5-of-staff-as-global-expansion-slows</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 08:20:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Nvidia 表示新芯片在预测令人失望后仍有望问世</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-20/nvidia-forecast-fails-to-meet-the-loftiest-estimates-for-ai-star</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Nvidia Corp. 向投资者保证，其新的产品阵容可以维持公司由人工智能推动的增长势头，尽管匆忙推出芯片的成本比预期的要高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-20/nvidia-forecast-fails-to-meet-the-loftiest-estimates-for-ai-star</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Nov 2024 21:22:43 GMT</pubDate>
